{"tid":806252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"免牢獄之災 摩佬書面親承稅務欺詐","createTime":"2018-09-04T13:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T16:16:06.000Z","uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7005083a971734dcda8d9ffa62bb8175cc7ba94e","tid":806252,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">前英超盟主</span>曼聯教練摩連奴此前被指控逃稅一事似乎終於要塵埃落定了。據西班牙《馬卡報》報導，摩連奴選擇用繳納罰款的方式免除牢獄之災。<br />\n<br />\n　　報導中稱，這件案子將於幾天后在馬德里法庭開庭審理。但是摩連奴已經與西班牙稅務機關達成協議，他將在開庭時以書面形式承認他隱瞞了自己2011年和2012年價值330萬歐元的肖像權收入。他將被判處為期1年的監禁。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/213648_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F213648_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=52df9543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過為了免除監禁，摩連奴將效仿許多有過類似經歷的球員，繳納罰款，罰款的數額為66.9萬歐元。在支付了這筆錢之後，他的案子將完全了結。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/213747_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F213747_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=cd410610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/213803_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F213803_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=698e2ad6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c37a599dac5ef61c92c99a2da784483a1d07328f","tid":806252,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T13:39:08.000Z","msg":"daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c648bbaec31467a799703e1b4362075c0444c30","tid":806252,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/214453_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F214453_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=65287edb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90276c1b7680f90992b154de562e5376953e3feb","tid":806252,"uid":151982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"前英超盟主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2def96ab1cf0a4c1b053a5a8e201cccc4f066814","tid":806252,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:16:06.000Z","msg":"條撚樣出街食飯無錢找西班牙數？"}]}